{"name": "odoo-addon-pos-partner-location-abstract", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-pos-partner-location-abstract", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/pos", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "POS Partner Location Abstract", "upload_time": 1712207758}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fpos-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/pos\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/pos/tree/16.0/pos_partner_location_abstract\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/pos-16-0/pos-16-0-pos_partner_location_abstract\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/pos&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# POS Partner Location Abstract\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:a9eae0fc2c410a71ba3062148599802fe9f4f89143bb1e37d0b78b60f9542daa\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module implements base functionality for using different map providers in POS.\nIt allows to select partner location directly on a map and stores selected location in the res.partner model.\nIt also tries to evaluate partner's address from coordinates and provides a helper function that generates location QR code.\n\nNB: This is a core module which is meant to be used in further customisations.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\nAs for the release date module `pos_partner_location_google_map` supports only Google Maps API.\n\nContribute to this module by adding other provider such as OpenStreetMap.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/pos/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/pos/issues/new?body=module:%20pos_partner_location_abstract%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Cetmix\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Cetmix \\<<https://cetmix.com/>>\n\n  - Ivan Sokolov\n  - Maksim Shurupov\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/pos](https://github.com/OCA/pos/tree/16.0/pos_partner_location_abstract) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_session", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2023 Cetmix O\u00dc", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_session.PosSession", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_session.PosSession._loader_params_res_partner", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_session.PosSession._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.address_struct", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models..address_struct", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_config", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models..pos_config", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_session", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models..pos_session", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.res_partner", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models..res_partner", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partner_location_abstract.models.pos_config", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2023 Cetmix O\u00dc", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.pos_partne